node.text: This Interfaith Heathen loves your message!
@wardoftheworld as an atheist I feel like you feel.
Unity vs Conformity.

@bearddisciple here’s what we say: if they can’t embrace our approach to inclusivity of our church, there are literally 100 churches within a 10 mile radius they can go to AND, I always help them/recommend churches to them. But there’s only 2 churches within that 10 mile radius that’s inclusive and a safe space for many marginalized folks. I fully understand that our work may not be for certain people. And that’s okay.
@joseph.yoo I understand why it is better to be inclusive. You can include all. The love of God is for all.
Well said. Either the lgbt flag in your background do you apply that to Christian’s who believe differently then you on those issues?
@laneuropicante stay warm!
💯 this was a great video, thank you! I’m also local to you 🤓
@mikeolbinski 🫰🫰🙏
@jaybakker 😍😍🥰🥰🫰🫰
Good stuff
“Unity: let’s walk together” 💯💯💯
@thereallouisjr 🤣🤣🤣
I want to type “I agree” but I can’t tell if tts a trap.
@wardoftheworld same. Like I could go here and listen without spazing out if it stays logical
@mskays_jewels  I’m with ya! 😂👏
@wardoftheworld as an atheist I feel like you feel.
As an atheist, I love this message.
👏bravo thank you ! Unity love ! 🙌🙌
Word!!!👏👏
This is a the most powerful statement I have heard! Thank you for passing along your wisdom.
🙌🙌 Preach indeed! 🙌🙌please keep your content going - messages just like these is what should be flooding our feeds. ❤️
Woooo!!!
Well said. Thank you for your message.
Thank you pastor for such spot on truths - I left my church for many of the reasons you consistently point out and wish more congregations had better leaders like you.  Keep doing Gods good work
PREACH 🙌🏼
I ❤️ your way of explaining scripture and putting in layman terms. We don't have to agree with everything to unite together. Father Yoo, thank you for your beautiful message.  Blessings 🙌
YESSSS!!! Thank you for speaking the truth in love! 🙏🫶🙏🫶
Love message
I plan on using this in my creative writing class this week. Thank you!

I too am no longer a “believer” because of the lies, judgment, cruelty, lack of compassion and hypocrisy, but it does my heart good to see people truly living up to the standards they claim to believe in.  This is very hopeful. 👏

I am not a ''believer'' but I swear this is one of my favorite ig pages. If I was raised around a religious leader like you sir....I'd definitely ''conform'' to your belief system 😉. Forreal thank you sir.
